<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; background:#6699FF; padding:0.2em; line-height:1.2em;">Holding</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:0; line-height:1.2em; vertical-align:middle;">The Court declared <a href="/wiki/Virginia" title="Virginia">Virginia</a>'s <a href="/wiki/Anti-miscegenation_statute" title="Anti-miscegenation statute" class="mw-redirect">anti-miscegenation statute</a>, the "<a href="/wiki/Racial_Integrity_Act_of_1924" title="Racial Integrity Act of 1924">Racial Integrity Act of 1924</a>", unconstitutional, thereby ending all <a href="/wiki/Race_(classification_of_human_beings)" title="Race (classification of human beings)">race</a>-based legal restriction on <a href="/wiki/Marriage" title="Marriage">marriage</a> in the <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a>.</td>
</tr>
